# Terraform/Terragrunt Ignores

# 1. Terraform State and Crash Files
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
.terraform/

# 2. Terraform Dependency Lock File (Requested)
# This file tracks provider and module versions. Ignore if you manage
# dependencies outside of the main repository.
.terraform.lock.hcl

# 3. Terragrunt Cache (Requested)
# Recursively ignore the local cache directory created by terragrunt
# when it downloads configurations.
**/.terragrunt-cache/

# 4. Terraform Provider Directories (Requested)
# Recursively ignore the downloaded provider binaries within .terraform/
# This ensures that even if a .terraform/ directory exists, the large
# provider downloads are excluded.
.terraform/providers/

# 5. Backup Files and Logs
*.backup
*.log
